cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.DS 

This paper presents a technique for improving the convergence of value iteration for POMDPs, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The technique involves modifying the value iteration algorithm, which is a common optimization technique in robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper presents experimental results on several test problems, which is a common approach in data science (cs.DS).
